@startuml
title Add Camera to Favorites - Activity Diagram

legend left
= Steps (must map to actions) =
1.⁠ ⁠User opens the platform
2.⁠ ⁠User logs in (required for favorites)
3.⁠ ⁠System shows "Favorites" button
4.⁠ ⁠User navigates to a camera (map/camera page)
5.⁠ ⁠User clicks "Add to Favorites" or "Remove from Favorites"
6.⁠ ⁠System updates favorites list
7.⁠ ⁠System confirms update and refreshes favorites view
endlegend

partition "User" {
  start
  :1. Open platform;
  :2. Log in;
}

partition "System" {
  :3. Show "Favorites" button;
}

partition "User" {
  :4. Navigate to a camera\n(via map/camera list);
  :5. Choose:\nAdd or Remove favorite;
}

partition "System" {
  if (Add favorite?) then (Add)
    :6. Add camera to favorites list;
  else (Remove)
    :6. Remove camera from favorites list;
  endif
  :7. Confirm update\nand refresh favorites view;
  stop
}
@enduml